                                                  Chapter 3
                                             Chernobyl-4

          Chernobyl-4 is a city adjacent to the CAZ. Peaceful civilians, military, and stalkers live here. 
          The city is small and you can walk around it in literally 3-4 minutes. I advise spending an hour or two getting to know the city. And I'll give you a very useful tip. Don't flash your patch in the city, the law enforcement... will have a couple of questions for you.
          And if you still have questions about where things are, I suggest you install the Discord messenger on your PDA. There, in the chat for not-so-important messages (offtopic), enter and send this link:
        https://discord.com/channels/1148992175347089468/1158795432831504537/1234967195650363533
        By following it, you will find a map of the city.

